\v 28 「​<a name="00700502800016" ll="SDBH:סִיסְרָא:000000">西西拉</a>​的​<a name="00700502800014" ll="SDBH:אֵם:000000">母親</a>​從​<a name="00700502800006" ll="SDBH:חַלֹּון:000000">窗戶</a>​裏​<a name="00700502800008" ll="SDBH:שׁקף:000000">往</a>​<a name="00700502800008" ll="SDBH:שׁקף:000000">外</a>​<a name="00700502800008" ll="SDBH:שׁקף:000000">觀看</a>​，​她​在​<a name="00700502800022" ll="SDBH:אֶשְׁנָב:000000">窗格子</a>​中​<a name="00700502800012" ll="SDBH:יבב:000000;SDBH:יבב:001000" tl="HOTTP869">哀號</a>​：​​『他​的​<a name="00700502800028" ll="SDBH:רֶכֶב:001001">戰車</a>​<a name="00700502800024" ll="SDBH:מַדּוּעַ:000000">為何</a>​<a name="00700502800026" ll="SDBH:בושׁ:002000">遲遲</a>​未​<a name="00700502800032">歸</a>​？​他​的​<a name="00700502800038;00700502800040" ll="SDBH:מֶרְכָּבָה:000000">車輪</a>​<a name="00700502800034" ll="SDBH:מַדּוּעַ:000000">為何</a>​<a name="00700502800036" ll="SDBH:אחר:000000">走</a>​<a name="00700502800036" ll="SDBH:אחר:000000">得</a>​那麼​<a name="00700502800036" ll="SDBH:אחר:000000">慢</a>​呢​？​』
    
\v 29 她​<a name="00700502900002" ll="SDBH:חָכָם, קסם:000000">聰明</a>​的​<a name="00700502900004" ll="SDBH:שָׂרָה:000000">宮女</a>​<a name="00700502900006" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">回答</a>​她​，​她​也​<a name="00700502900012;00700502900014" ll="SDBH:אֵמֶר:000000;SDBH:שׁוב:000050">自言自語</a>​說​：
    
\v 30 『​或許​他們​<a name="00700503000006" ll="SDBH:מצא:000000">得</a>​了​<a name="00700503000010" ll="SDBH:שָׁלָל:000000">戰利品</a>​而​<a name="00700503000008" ll="SDBH:חלק:000006">分</a>​，​<a name="00700503000018" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000000">每</a>​<a name="00700503000018" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000000">個</a>​<a name="00700503000020" ll="SDBH:גֶּבֶר:000000">壯士</a>​得​了​一兩個​<a name="00700503000012;00700503000014" ll="SDBH:רַחֲמָה:000000">女子</a>​？​
    <a name="00700503000028" ll="SDBH:סִיסְרָא:000000" il="Satellite Bible Atlas00046" tl="HOTTP870">西西拉</a>​得​了​<a name="00700503000024" ll="SDBH:צֶבַע:000000" tl="HOTTP870">彩衣</a>​為​<a name="00700503000022" ll="SDBH:שָׁלָל:000000" tl="HOTTP870">擄物</a>​，​得​了​<a name="00700503000034" ll="SDBH:רִקְמָה:000000" il="EmbroideredCloth-01-056" tl="HOTTP870">繡花</a>​<a name="00700503000034" ll="SDBH:רִקְמָה:000000" il="EmbroideredCloth-01-056" tl="HOTTP870">的</a>​<a name="00700503000032" ll="SDBH:צֶבַע:000000" tl="HOTTP870">彩衣</a>​為​<a name="00700503000030" ll="SDBH:שָׁלָל:000000" tl="HOTTP870">掠物</a>​，​這​兩​面​<a name="00700503000038" ll="SDBH:רִקְמָה:000000" il="EmbroideredCloth-01-056" tl="HOTTP870">繡花</a>​的​<a name="00700503000036" ll="SDBH:צֶבַע:000000" tl="HOTTP870">彩衣</a>​，​披​在​<a name="00700503000042" ll="SDBH:צַוָּאר:000000" tl="HOTTP871">頸項</a>​上​作為​<a name="00700503000044" ll="SDBH:שָׁלָל:000000" tl="HOTTP871">戰利品</a>​。​』
    
\v 31 「​<a name="00700503100010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">耶和華</a>​啊​，​願​你​的​<a name="00700503100008" ll="SDBH:איב:000001">仇敵</a>​<a name="00700503100006">都</a>​<a name="00700503100002">這樣</a>​<a name="00700503100004" ll="SDBH:אבד:000004">滅亡</a>​！​願​<a name="00700503100014" ll="SDBH:אהב:000001">愛</a>​你​的​人​如​<a name="00700503100022" ll="SDBH:שֶׁמֶשׁ:000000">太陽</a>​<a name="00700503100018" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">上升</a>​，​<a name="00700503100026" ll="SDBH:גְּבוּרָה:000000">大</a>​<a name="00700503100026" ll="SDBH:גְּבוּרָה:000000">發</a>​<a name="00700503100026" ll="SDBH:גְּבוּרָה:000000">光輝</a>​！​」​於是​這​<a name="00700503100034" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">地</a>​<a name="00700503100030" ll="SDBH:שׁקט:000001">太平</a>​<a name="00700503100036" ll="SDBH:אַרְבַּע:000001">四十</a>​<a name="00700503100038" ll="SDBH:שָׁנָה:000000">年</a>​。
